        Apply microservices and TDD makes enterprises more productive.
        
        - Show all callable commands.
        
        ./setup.py
        
        - Install packages.
        
        ./setup.py develop
        
        - Run some services.
        
        ./setup.py run user
        
        - Run unit tests.
        
        ./setup.py test
        
        - Run system test.
        
        ./setup.py sys
        
        
        
